VALUES

('pandadoc',
 'PandaDoc',
 'Create, send, and e-sign proposals, contracts, and quotes with AI-powered automation',
 'PandaDoc is a document automation and e-signature platform used by over 50,000 businesses to create, send, and track proposals, quotes, contracts, and onboarding documents. The platform includes an AI content assistant that helps draft proposal sections, suggest pricing structures, and generate product descriptions from a brief input. Templates cover the most common business document types - sales proposals, service agreements, NDAs, statements of work, and HR documents - and are customisable with drag-and-drop fields for text, images, pricing tables, and e-signature fields. Once a document is sent, PandaDoc tracks exactly when the recipient opened it, which sections they spent time on, and whether they forwarded it to another stakeholder, giving the sending team real-time visibility into deal engagement. The built-in e-signature is legally binding in most jurisdictions and requires no additional subscription. PandaDoc integrates with Salesforce, HubSpot, Pipedrive, and other CRMs to pull contact and deal data directly into documents, eliminating copy-paste errors. For teams that send a high volume of proposals or contracts, PandaDoc reduces the time from deal agreement to signed document from days to minutes. The free plan includes unlimited document uploads and e-signatures with basic features, making it accessible for freelancers and small teams before committing to a paid plan.',
 NULL,
 'https://pandadoc.com',
 'https://pandadoc.com',
