('proposify',
 'Proposify',
 'Proposal software with templates, e-signature, and engagement analytics for closing deals faster',
 'Proposify is a proposal management platform built for sales teams and agencies that send high volumes of proposals to prospective clients. The core product is a template-based proposal builder where teams create a master proposal template covering the cover page, scope of work, pricing, terms, and case studies, then generate client-specific versions in minutes by customising the relevant sections. The platform tracks proposal opens, page-by-page time spent, and signature status in real time, giving sales managers visibility into where deals are stalling. Proposify includes an electronic signature workflow and a client portal where prospects can comment on specific sections before signing. The built-in content library stores approved copy, images, pricing options, and legal terms that any team member can pull into a new proposal, ensuring consistency and brand compliance across the whole team. Approval workflows allow managers to review and sign off on non-standard pricing or terms before a proposal goes out. The analytics dashboard shows which templates have the highest close rates and which sections prospects skip, allowing ongoing improvement of proposal content. Proposify is particularly strong for agencies selling services at volume - marketing agencies, design studios, consulting firms, and IT services companies - where consistent, professional proposals are a meaningful competitive advantage. Pricing starts at $49 per user per month with no free tier.',
 NULL,
 'https://proposify.com',
