('qwilr',
 'Qwilr',
 'Turn proposals into interactive web pages that track engagement and accept payment',
 'Qwilr turns traditional PDF proposals into interactive web pages that feel modern, branded, and engaging to the recipient. Instead of sending a static document, Qwilr proposals are live web pages that load in any browser without a download, include embedded videos, interactive pricing configurators, and live content that can be updated even after sending. The interactive pricing feature is particularly distinctive - prospects can toggle between package options, add services, and see the total update in real time before accepting. Qwilr tracks every visit to the proposal page, showing when the recipient opened it, how long they spent on each section, and whether they shared it with colleagues. When the prospect is ready, they accept the proposal directly in the web page with a click without printing, signing, or scanning. Qwilr integrates with HubSpot, Salesforce, and Pipedrive to pull deal and contact data directly, and webhooks trigger CRM updates when a proposal is accepted. The template library covers common proposal types for agencies, SaaS companies, consultants, and professional services firms. Qwilr also accepts payment directly within the proposal page through Stripe integration, allowing clients to pay a deposit or full amount at the moment of acceptance without a separate invoice workflow. Qwilr web-based proposals tend to produce higher engagement and faster acceptance compared to PDF proposals, particularly with buyers who are used to modern SaaS experiences.',
 NULL,
 'https://qwilr.com',
 'https://qwilr.com',
