('dealhub',
 'DealHub',
 'Revenue platform with CPQ, contract management, and digital sales rooms for B2B teams',
 'DealHub is a revenue platform that combines configure-price-quote (CPQ), contract management, and digital sales rooms in a single platform for B2B sales teams. The CPQ module handles complex product configurations and pricing rules, ensuring sales reps can generate accurate quotes for configurable products without errors or manual spreadsheets. Once a quote is approved, DealHub generates a contract and presents it alongside the quote in a shared digital sales room where both the sales team and the buyer can collaborate, comment, and negotiate terms without long email chains. The digital sales room provides a single URL for all deal-related content - proposals, case studies, technical documentation, pricing, and the contract - accessible to the buyer team throughout the sales cycle. DealHub uses AI to suggest the next best actions for stalled deals, identify risk signals from buyer behaviour, and recommend upsell opportunities based on deal context. The platform integrates deeply with Salesforce, HubSpot, and Microsoft Dynamics to ensure deal data stays synchronised across the revenue tech stack. Subscription management features handle recurring revenue changes - upgrades, downgrades, mid-term amendments, and renewals - without manual intervention from the finance team. DealHub is targeted at mid-market and enterprise B2B companies with complex product catalogues and multi-stakeholder sales cycles where accuracy, speed, and buyer experience all matter together.',
 NULL,
 'https://dealhub.io',
 'https://dealhub.io',
