('oneflow',
 'Oneflow',
 'Contract management platform that turns contracts into live digital documents for faster signing',
 'Oneflow is a contract management platform that reimagines how business contracts work. Rather than static PDF documents that get emailed back and forth, Oneflow contracts are live digital documents that both parties can edit, negotiate, and sign in real time within a shared online workspace. The platform covers the full contract lifecycle - creating from templates, negotiating with tracked changes and comments, approving through internal workflows, collecting e-signatures, and storing in a searchable archive with automated renewal reminders. The template library includes standard business contracts across sales, HR, and procurement use cases, all customisable with variable fields that pull data from integrated CRM or HR systems. Oneflow AI assists with contract drafting by suggesting standard clauses, flagging missing required fields, and summarising contract terms in plain language for non-legal reviewers. The audit trail captures every change, comment, and approval action with timestamps, providing a complete history for compliance purposes. Oneflow integrates with Salesforce, HubSpot, Pipedrive, SuperOffice, and Microsoft 365. The live document format is particularly effective at reducing the negotiation cycle - both parties can propose changes inside the document and see each other''s edits in real time, removing the confusion of document version management by email. Free plan available for small teams with a limited monthly contract volume; paid plans from $38 per user per month.',
 NULL,
 'https://oneflow.com',
