('juro',
 'Juro',
 'AI-native contract management platform for legal and business teams to move faster on contracts',
 'Juro is an AI-native contract management platform built for legal and business teams that want to reduce contract turnaround time without sacrificing accuracy. The platform distinguishes itself from traditional contract management tools by treating contracts as structured data rather than documents - every clause, obligation, and commercial term is stored as a searchable, reportable data point rather than text buried in a PDF. This approach lets legal teams answer questions like "which contracts include a most-favoured-nation clause" or "which supplier agreements renew in Q3" in seconds, without manual document review. Juro AI assists with contract generation by drafting standard agreements from a business brief, suggesting appropriate clauses for the contract type, and flagging terms that create unusual risk compared to the company playbook. The self-service workflow allows business teams in sales, HR, and procurement to generate routine contracts independently using approved templates, reducing the volume of low-complexity requests that reach the legal team. Electronic signature is built in without requiring a separate tool. Juro integrates with Salesforce, Greenhouse, BambooHR, and Slack, connecting contracts to the systems where business teams already work. The platform is particularly strong for legal teams managing a high volume of similar contract types such as NDAs, employment agreements, and vendor contracts, where a consistent, scalable process matters more than custom document handling. Pricing is available on request.',
 NULL,
 'https://juro.com',
 'https://juro.com',
