('better-proposals',
 'Better Proposals',
 'Proposal software for freelancers and agencies to create, send, and get paid faster',
 'Better Proposals is a proposal software tool built for freelancers, agencies, and small businesses that need to create professional, branded proposals quickly and close deals faster. The platform is built around simplicity - a straightforward template editor, a library of industry-specific proposal templates, and built-in electronic signature and payment processing that lets clients accept and pay in a single step. Unlike enterprise proposal tools, Better Proposals is priced and designed for individual contributors and small teams: the interface is learnable in an afternoon, templates are ready to use with minimal customisation, and the per-user pricing is affordable at team scale. The AI writing assistant helps draft proposal sections including executive summaries, scope of work descriptions, and pricing justifications from a brief description of the project. Proposal analytics track when clients open the proposal, how long they spend on each section, and when they share it with a colleague, giving the sender the right moment to follow up. Better Proposals integrates with Stripe and PayPal for payment collection, and with HubSpot, Pipedrive, and Zapier for CRM and workflow automation. The template library covers marketing agencies, web designers, consultants, coaches, and freelancers across dozens of verticals. Free trial available; paid plans start at $19 per user per month, making it one of the most affordable full-featured proposal tools available for independent professionals.',
 NULL,
