('loopio',
 'Loopio',
 'RFP response platform that automates answers with a searchable library of approved content',
 'Loopio is a response management platform designed for teams that respond to RFPs (Requests for Proposal), RFIs (Requests for Information), and security questionnaires at volume. Responding to RFPs manually is one of the most time-consuming activities in enterprise sales and procurement teams, involving copying answers from previous responses, finding the right subject matter expert, formatting to match the RFP template, and ensuring consistency across a document that may have hundreds of questions. Loopio addresses this by building a searchable library of approved responses - a content repository where every answer is tagged, attributed to a subject matter expert, and set with an expiry date to ensure it remains current. When a new RFP arrives, Loopio AI automatically matches questions to existing library responses and pre-fills the document, allowing the team to review and refine rather than write from scratch. The collaboration workflow routes unanswered or outdated questions to the appropriate expert within the platform, with deadline tracking and completion status visible to the project manager. Loopio integrates with Salesforce to link RFP projects to CRM opportunities and with Microsoft Office and Google Drive for document export. The platform tracks answer currency, flagging responses that have not been updated within a configurable timeframe, so the library does not drift out of date as products and policies change. Used by sales, proposal management, and pre-sales teams at mid-market and enterprise companies where RFP response volume is high enough to justify a dedicated workflow.',
 NULL,
 'https://loopio.com',
